        "@value": "Celebrate the end of an incredible season with ENCORE, the Queen’s Competitive Dance Team’s annual year‑end showcase. This energetic event highlights the talent, dedication, and artistry of the team, featuring all 19 competitive group routines along with 8 captivating graduate solos. Join us for an evening of powerful choreography, dynamic performances, and a vibrant celebration of the dancers’ hard work throughout the year."
      }
