        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "Classic Albums Live - Slippery When Wet"
      }
    ],
    "https://ogp.me/ns#description": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "Get ready to rock as Classic Albums Live brings Bon Jovi’s iconic Slippery When Wet album to life—note for note, cut for cut—live on stage! This electrifying performance will transport you back to 1986, as a roster of world-class musicians recreates hits like “Livin’ on a Prayer,” “You Give Love a Bad Name,” and “Wanted Dead or Alive” with astonishing precision and passion. Followed by a greatest hits set."
      }
    ],
    "https://ogp.me/ns#image": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
