        "@value": "Stones in my Shoes II"
      }
    ],
    "https://ogp.me/ns#description": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "Join us at Homestead Baby Grand Theatre for an intimate evening with Gordon Desveaux, returning to the stage with his newest live performance, Stones in My Shoes II. Known for heartfelt storytelling and expressive guitar work, Desveaux brings his signature blend of warmth, reflection, and acoustic artistry to this limited‑seat event."
      }
    ],
